[
  "Chairman emeritus of Indian consumer goods outfit Dabur, Vivek Chand Burman, is the oldest member of the founding Burman clan.\r\n",
  "Dabur was founded by his great-grandfather in 1884 to sell ayurvedic medicines. ",
  "He joined the company in 1954 and became chairman in 1998 holding that post for close to a decade. ",
  "In 2007, he handed over charge to nephew Anand Burman, who is also a billionaire.",
  "His son, Mohit, was appointed vice-chairman of Dabur in July 2019."
]